linguaedit (1.8.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Rewritten video preview: 16:9 aspect, full transport controls, subtitle overlay
  * Live-update translation column in tree view while typing
  * Extended selection (Shift+click, Ctrl+click) in tree view
  * Resizable column headers
  * Unity MonoBehaviour localization table parser
  * Fixed QThread SIGABRT crash (replaced with daemon threading.Thread)
  * Fixed macOS SIGSEGV crash (disabled Qt accessibility)
  * Fixed SRT/VTT subtitle roundtrip, dark mode contrast, multi-selection crash
  * Fixed locale deprecation warning for Python 3.13+

 -- Daniel Nylander <daniel@danielnylander.se>  Fri, 13 Feb 2026 03:00:00 +0100

linguaedit (1.3.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Cross-platform credential storage (Keychain/Credential Locker/Secret Service)
  * Video preview synced with subtitle editing
  * Concordance search, segment split/merge
  * UI: progress ring, minimap, context panel, quick actions
  * Security: XXE protection in all XML parsers
  * Bug fixes: RESX, Apple Strings, Unity Asset parsers

